      </p>
      <p>
        The dehumidifier is sized to match your crawl space square footage, air volume, and
        real-world moisture load. Oversized units short-cycle without maintaining consistent
        humidity. Undersized units run continuously and never reach target levels. Proper sizing is
        what separates a system that works from one that wastes energy.
      </p>
      <p>
        Every installation uses Energy Star certified, commercial-grade equipment built for
        continuous crawl space operation. We route a permanent condensate drain line — fully
        automatic, no buckets, no manual emptying — and verify the system holds 45–50% RH before we
